=== Siege on Paradise ===
[[File:Evt astral rift siege on paradise baol.png|450px|thumb|The Baol world on other side of the astral rift]]
Siege on Paradise leads to an alternate universe where the Baol are still alive.
: 1. '''''Siege on Paradise''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}, choice:
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3 ''"Contact the planet's inhabitants."''
:* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3 ''"Contact the orbiting fleet."''
: Contacted the planet's inhabitats (the Baol):
:: 2. '''''Meeting the Baol / Plantoid Encounter''''': ''"Disclose what we know of the Baol." / "We are explorers."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:: 3. '''''Impending Doom / A Request for Aid''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 3 ''"We will help however we can."'', proceed to '''''Saving the Baol / Considering Options'''''
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"It is not our place to interfere"'', proceed to '''''Not Our Fight'''''
::: 4. '''''Not Our Fight''''', ''""Prepare observation satellites."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
::: 5. '''''Ashes to Ashes''''', ''"This is a unique research opportunity."'', ends the rift, creates a {{icon|society}} 25 society research deposit on the astral rift. After 2-4 years, triggers the '''''Dust to Dust''''' event:
:::* '''''Dust to Dust''''', gives {{iconify|society}} and {{iconify|engineering}} research, removes the society research deposit from the rift.
:: 4. '''''Saving the Baol / Considering Options''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Genetically modify the Baol."'', proceed to '''''Genetic Reinforcement''''' (requires {{iconify|Gene Tailoring|22px}})
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Deploy experimental planetary cloaking."'', pay {{icon|astral threads}} {{red|50}} astral threads, proceed to '''''Under the Radar''''' (requires {{iconify|Basic Cloaking Fields|22px}})
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Generate an astral shield."'', pay {{icon|astral threads}} {{red|100}} astral threads, proceed to '''''Astral Shield''''' (unavailable if has both of the above technologies)
::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 ''"Preserve the seedlings."'', proceed to '''''Life Finds a Way'''''
:: 5. Final outcome:
