::Regardless of outcome, gives {{reward|ast|ast3|empty|empty}}, ends the rift.
: Contacted the orbiting fleet (the Grunur):
:: 2. '''''Flagship Escort''''', ''"Let us see where this leads..."'' / ''"The Grunur are dangerous. Be cautious."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:: 3. '''''A Unique Conversation''''', ''"We are explorers."'' / ''"We are explorers, and we have seen your future."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:: {{yellow|IF Discovered the Baol precursor:}}
::: 4. '''''The Infamous Grunur''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Share rare military technology with the Grunur."'', proceed to '''''Sharing of Knowledge''''' (requires a rare technology such as {{iconify|Artificial Dragonscales|22px|suf=tech}}, {{iconify|Dark Matter Propulsion|22px}}, or {{iconify|Jump Drive|22px|suf=tech}})
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 4 ''"Share Baol research data with the Grunur."'', proceed to '''''Bearing Witness'''''
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 2 ''"Refuse to co-operate."'', proceed to '''''Expedition's End'''''
::: 5. '''''Sharing of Knowledge''''', ''"A worthy exchange."'', gives 25% progress towards a random {{iconify|Military Theory}} technology, proceed to '''''Grunur Weapons Interface'''''
::: 5. '''''Bearing Witness''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 4 ''"Watch the extermination."'', proceed to '''''Watching a World Burn'''''
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Refuse."'', proceed to '''''Expedition's End'''''
:: {{yellow|Did not discover the Baol precursor:}}
::: 4. '''''A Meek Introduction''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Respond with bravado. Do not be intimidated."'', proceed to '''''Taking a Stand'''''
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Attempt to reason with them."'', proceed to '''''Punishment'''''
::: 5. '''''Taking a Stand''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty normal}} 4 ''"Press the crystal. Order the launch."'', proceed to '''''Watching a World Burn'''''
:::* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Refuse."'', proceed to '''''Expedition's End'''''
::: 5. '''''Punishment''''', ''"Remain strong. We will find a way to recover you."'', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}, proceed to '''''Expedition's End'''''
:: 6. Final outcome:
:: {| class="wikitable plainlist"
! Outcome
! Effect
|-
| '''''Grunur Weapons Interface'''''
| 
* ''Grunur Weapons Interface'' modifier: 
* {{icon|ship fire rate}} {{green|+10%}} Ship Fire Rate
|-
| '''''Watching a World Burn'''''
|
* {{reward|soc|rsh3}}
* [[File:Army flamestorm.png|24px|link=Armies#Flamestorm Troopers|Flamestorm Troopers]] Unlocks the ability to recruit Flamestorm Troopers.
|-
| '''''Expedition's End'''''
|
* {{reward|eng|rsh3}}
* Scientist is lost for 5-7 years.
|}
:: Regardless of outcome, gives {{reward|ast|ast3|empty|empty}}, ends the rift.
If the rift concluded with the '''''Expedition's End''''' outcome, get '''''[leader name] Returns''''' event in 5-7 years:
* Leader comes back with the {{iconify|Rift Warped}} trait. They gain the {{trait|Expertise: Propulsion|w=24px|class=Scientist|bg=eng|veteran=yes|tier=1}} Expertise: Propulsion I trait if they do not have it, otherwise they gain the {{trait|Expertise: Voidcraft|w=24px|class=Scientist|bg=eng|veteran=yes|tier=1}} Expertise: Voidcraft I trait. If the leader already has both traits, no other trait is given.
